"Ya Tuhan, mohon berkati kami semua."

00:06:38.600 --> 00:06:40.920
Jangan sentuh aku, Rahul.

00:06:46.440 --> 00:06:49.360
“Salam Krishna,
Govinda, Hari, Murari.”

